Package: periodization
Title: Creates a Visual Representation of a Sport Periodization and Calculate the ACWR
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jorge R",
             "Fernandez-Santos",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "jorgedelrosario.fernandez@uca.es",
             comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-5047-2976"))
Description: Creates a high quality visual representation of a sport training periodization. Additionally,
             the package has functions to calculate the Acute Chronic Workload Ratio following three different
             methods: Exponentially Weighted Moving Average (EWMA), Rolling Average Couple (RAC) and Rolling Average 
             Uncouple (RAU).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
